🐛 Common Issues
Issue: “Build Failed”
Solution: Check build logs in Vercel dashboard. Usually a dependency issue.
Issue: “Blank Page After Deploy”
Solution: Check browser console. Usually a routing issue.
	∙	Verify vercel.json is in root directory
	∙	Clear browser cache
Issue: API Keys Not Saving
Solution: API keys are stored in memory only (by design for security)
	∙	Re-enter keys each session
	∙	Consider using environment variables for auto-fill
🔒 Security Best Practices
	∙	✅ Never commit API keys to GitHub
	∙	✅ Use .gitignore (already included)
	∙	✅ Start with Paper Trading
	∙	✅ Enable 2FA on Vercel account
	∙	✅ Use environment variables for sensitive data
